          RELEASE NOTES:

          The titans who hold the sky are about to drop it. A trio of
        heroes: beautiful and clever Leada, mighty Protus and nimble
        Adoris embark on a quest to help the giants. In their journey
        they will visit amazing landmarks of the ancient world, encounter
        beautiful mythical creatures and make friends with gods and epic
        heroes.

        In this brand new time management game from Realore you can take
        control over three characters each with their special abilities.
        Use the power of gods to boost your progress through levels.
        Feast your eyes on the beautiful landscapes and set pieces.
